"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-17T16:55:47.000Z","msg":"保險公司卻要追收已發放給經紀的佣金。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6777cc2840121b7dd3888f4feab89ba2765f77b","tid":1972942,"uid":7957,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-18T07:29:58.000Z","msg":"如果收人減少 就可以申請援助<br />\n咁好多打工仔被減薪應該都要有資格申請援助<br />\n依家香港得保險業生活艱難？<br />\n識得財務規劃 但無預留幾個月人工 應付呢種情況<br />\n唔讀finance 既人都知咩叫 emergency fund 啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n政府援助 被炒失業人士 好合理 但唔係收入減少既保險佬<br />\n要鬥慘 大把人慘過保險佬"},{"pid":"b115eec512c1c1bb2d3933841cb7406dc0615077","tid":1972942,"uid":9230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-18T15:03:06.000Z","msg":"後勤表示心涼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申：加咗人工出咗B仔"},{"pid":"d2b62ca6d08cd1150555c84e5a53452b0cf66de0","tid":1972942,"uid":180401,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-18T15:04:58.000Z","msg":"保險狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7da301b915434a34ce37797de2fdc47224ec2fe","tid":1972942,"uid":12034,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-18T15:06:43.000Z","msg":"日鳩人sale人強積金<br />\n<br />\n自己就無供<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f432b4a425fb51a0d7f8a6101c23944359a56975","tid":1972942,"uid":54126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c4510cb426aa6c6a384e866dcdae9ef4aca1f7b8","tid":1972942,"uid":227275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-17T16:55:47.000Z","msg":"保險公司卻要追收已發放給經紀的佣金。<br />\n<br />\n<im